{"tid":203363,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"GLC 43 vs F Pace","createTime":"2017-04-16T08:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T01:15:49.000Z","uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4293b05be127cb997ee55a22ef658ec822f42073","tid":203363,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"兩部都係3.0 V6 大家都係三百幾匹<br />\n邊部好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nF Pace 連埋option 78萬 啲option都好似幾豐富<br />\n而GLC 43 淨車價 84萬 (如果要加option要加啲咩)<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇 有冇用家"},{"pid":"372a00b3fe0edf32449e20476eb3ba43cffbc83a","tid":203363,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"新benz 如果有得揀:<br />\n1. intelligence drive+safety <br />\n2.burmester 一定要升, 出去搞點到去唔到原廠個平衡<br />\n其他冇所謂, 43好多都standard<br />\n<br />\n唔係建議你買benz, 只係講自己經驗<br />\njaguar 唔熟答你唔到"},{"pid":"ca664e8b50b3ec1a655fe31d19b62a92c848e110","tid":203363,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:46:33.000Z","msg":"F pace 剛剛拎左2017 world card of the year.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見d試車片好正 有錢都想買部"},{"pid":"2c399c4482da1877aa0914c2109fab77fe471ed7","tid":203363,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新benz 如果有得揀:<br />\n1. intelligence drive+safety <br />\n2.burmester 一定要升, 出去搞點到去唔到原廠個平衡<br />\n其他冇所謂, 43好多都standard<br />\n<br />\n唔係建議你買benz, 只係講自己經驗<br />\njaguar 唔熟答你唔到</blockquote><br />\nAMG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca98323c04240f0f7811f17cbeb85b86619b743","tid":203363,"uid":71207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>F pace 剛剛拎左2017 world card of the year.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見d試車片好正 有錢都想買部</blockquote><br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好抵<br />\n但聽人講內飾好多都係硬膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5151720c0120596a83744071440894cdd939f9c","tid":203363,"uid":46009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"GLC 43 未望過真車, 唔敢 comment<br />\n<br />\nF Pace 就上年試過車<br />\n呢口價買到呢架車堅係抵屌<br />\n3.0 V6 SC 340匹<br />\n講型: 英國血統SUV, 品味別樹一格<br />\n講實用: 空間夠用有餘, 實用性高<br />\n講豪華: 英式豪華, 未必拍得住 Benz, 但絕不失禮<br />\nGimmick: 淨係果舊波棍都夠晒亮點<br />\n<br />\n膠的確係有D 膠件, 不過印象中唔係全部都硬膠黎<br />\n呢架車最大的缺點係個中控同架 Land Rover DS 一樣太似樣<br />\n<br />\n利申: 無買"},{"pid":"a6fd78897923ad74dd5b6edbcc3b7358c7647172","tid":203363,"uid":46009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73cK1i9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73cK1i9.jpg&h=66c06db1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7Kr14A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7Kr14A.jpg&h=d2d16a20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/101753_bf02dbeb92a79ff2cc1a7bc5a075329a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F101753_bf02dbeb92a79ff2cc1a7bc5a075329a.jpg&h=d6b54311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補返幾張相"},{"pid":"331e793d195b255c9e7ce2386f3e47bacea31fbe","tid":203363,"uid":38394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"如果有得配f type既flat bottom肽盤就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4e6cc6d501c7564163947d027a233bc99cd95d","tid":203363,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73cK1i9.jpg\" data-thumbn